div.p:
Some developers prefer to work closely with
database drivers, writing their own SQL statements, as in
$results = $this->db->query(...);

Other developers prefer to use the 

                    Query Builder for
                a more O-O approach to database manipulation, as in

                $model->where(...);

                    $model->limit(...);

                    $results = $model->get();

div.code:
                class Sales extends MY_Model {

  function __construct() {

    parent::__construct();

  }



  function new_order(...) {}

  function add_item(...) {}

  function calc_tax(...) {}

  function receipt(...) {}



                }
